{
  "id": "ielts10_test4_s1",
  "title": "Cambridge IELTS 10 Test 4 Section 1",
  "audio": "ielts10_test4_s1.mp3",
  "parts": [
    {
      "name": "Section 1",
      "segments": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "start": 148.8,
          "end": 149.36,
          "text": "Thorndyke's"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "start": 149.98,
          "end": 152.68,
          "text": "Good morning. Is that Mr Thorndyke?"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "start": 153.02,
          "end": 154.58,
          "text": "Speaking. How can I help?"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "start": 155.2,
          "end": 162.2,
          "text": "I've got quite a few things which need painting and fixing in the flat and I wonder whether you'd be able to do the work."
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "start": 162.52,
          "end": 165.76,
          "text": "I'm sure I'd be able to help but let me take down a few details."
        },
        {
          "id": 6,
          "start": 166.42,
          "end": 167.18,
          "text": "Yes, of course."
        },
        {
          "id": 7,
          "start": 168.0,
          "end": 170.98,
          "text": "Well, firstly, how did you hear about us?"
        },
        {
          "id": 8,
          "start": 171.52,
          "end": 177.84,
          "text": "It was my friend May Hampton you did some excellent work for her a couple of years ago. Do you remember?"
        },
        {
          "id": 9,
          "start": 178.64,
          "end": 182.12,
          "text": "Oh, yes, that was in West Park Flats, lovely lady."
        },
        {
          "id": 10,
          "start": 182.48,
          "end": 183.4,
          "text": "Yes, she is."
        },
        {
          "id": 11,
          "start": 183.92,
          "end": 185.52,
          "text": "And what's your name, please?"
        },
        {
          "id": 12,
          "start": 186.08,
          "end": 187.52,
          "text": "It's Edith Pargetter."
        },
        {
          "id": 13,
          "start": 188.68,
          "end": 191.42,
          "text": "Edith can you spell your surname, please?"
        },
        {
          "id": 14,
          "start": 191.42,
          "end": 193.1,
          "text": "It's P-A-R-G-E-double T-E-R."
        },
        {
          "id": 15,
          "start": 198.2,
          "end": 201.94,
          "text": "Double T, right. And do you live in West Park Flats as well?"
        },
        {
          "id": 16,
          "start": 202.5,
          "end": 206.3,
          "text": "No, actually it's East Park, Flat 4."
        },
        {
          "id": 17,
          "start": 207.1,
          "end": 210.74,
          "text": "Oh, right, that's over the road, I seem to remember – quite difficult to get to."
        },
        {
          "id": 18,
          "start": 211.84,
          "end": 214.22,
          "text": "Yes, it's at the back of the library."
        },
        {
          "id": 19,
          "start": 214.78,
          "end": 217.8,
          "text": "Right, I know. And what's your phone number?"
        },
        {
          "id": 20,
          "start": 220.6,
          "end": 225.32,
          "text": "875934 but I'm out a great deal in the afternoons and evenings."
        },
        {
          "id": 21,
          "start": 225.82,
          "end": 228.7,
          "text": "So would the best time to ring you be in the morning?"
        },
        {
          "id": 22,
          "start": 229.14,
          "end": 229.4,
          "text": "Yes."
        },
        {
          "id": 23,
          "start": 229.92,
          "end": 239.36,
          "text": "Fine. I've made a note of that. Can I just ask, I'll be in a van and I know parking's rather difficult round your flats. Where would you recommend?"
        },
        {
          "id": 24,
          "start": 240.04,
          "end": 246.96,
          "text": "Well, I always tell people in larger vehicles to park by the postbox on the other side of the road from the entrance."
        },
        {
          "id": 25,
          "start": 248.18,
          "end": 249.18,
          "text": "Good, thanks."
        },
        {
          "id": 26,
          "start": 249.9,
          "end": 253.28,
          "text": "And will you be able to give me a full itemised quote?"
        },
        {
          "id": 27,
          "start": 253.74,
          "end": 257.36,
          "text": "Oh, yes, I'll list all the jobs separately with individual prices."
        },
        {
          "id": 28,
          "start": 258.14,
          "end": 259.12,
          "text": "That'd be a great help."
        },
        {
          "id": 29,
          "start": 259.58,
          "end": 260.02,
          "text": "No problem."
        },
        {
          "id": 31,
          "start": 307.8,
          "end": 309.78,
          "text": "Now, what would you like me to do?"
        },
        {
          "id": 32,
          "start": 310.68,
          "end": 320.48,
          "text": "Firstly and most urgently is in the kitchen. With all the weather damage, the glass in the door has cracked and I'd need that fixing"
        },
        {
          "id": 33,
          "start": 321.02,
          "end": 322.8,
          "text": "I presume you mean replacing?"
        },
        {
          "id": 34,
          "start": 323.38,
          "end": 325.66,
          "text": "Oh, yes. And as soon as possible"
        },
        {
          "id": 35,
          "start": 326.4,
          "end": 329.16,
          "text": "What I'll do is come round tomorrow morning and do that immediately."
        },
        {
          "id": 36,
          "start": 329.96,
          "end": 334.26,
          "text": "Thank you so much. The other things aren't so urgent but"
        },
        {
          "id": 37,
          "start": 334.26,
          "end": 336.9,
          "text": "Now, I'll make a note of everything you want doing."
        },
        {
          "id": 38,
          "start": 337.66,
          "end": 341.2,
          "text": "Well, in the kitchen I'd like some painting doing."
        },
        {
          "id": 39,
          "start": 341.86,
          "end": 342.96,
          "text": "All the kitchen walls?"
        },
        {
          "id": 40,
          "start": 343.42,
          "end": 347.0,
          "text": "Just the area over the cooker. It's very greasy"
        },
        {
          "id": 41,
          "start": 347.62,
          "end": 349.42,
          "text": "Right it does tend to get that way!"
        },
        {
          "id": 42,
          "start": 349.84,
          "end": 350.18,
          "text": "Yes!"
        },
        {
          "id": 43,
          "start": 351.2,
          "end": 358.08,
          "text": "Well, if you want a proper job done what I'd need to do is strip the old paint and plaster it about a week before I paint it."
        },
        {
          "id": 44,
          "start": 358.56,
          "end": 363.02,
          "text": "Of course. Now, May tells me you also do work in the garden."
        },
        {
          "id": 45,
          "start": 363.6,
          "end": 364.3,
          "text": "That's right."
        },
        {
          "id": 46,
          "start": 364.88,
          "end": 367.42,
          "text": "Well, I'd like you to replace a fence."
        },
        {
          "id": 47,
          "start": 367.9,
          "end": 368.66,
          "text": "Just one?"
        },
        {
          "id": 48,
          "start": 369.18,
          "end": 370.8,
          "text": "Yes, at the far end."
        },
        {
          "id": 49,
          "start": 371.3,
          "end": 372.48,
          "text": "Fine. Shouldn't be a problem."
        },
        {
          "id": 50,
          "start": 373.2,
          "end": 374.06,
          "text": "And that's the lot."
        },
        {
          "id": 51,
          "start": 374.7,
          "end": 379.38,
          "text": "Fine. Yeah, as I say I can come round tomorrow morning to look over things with you."
        },
        {
          "id": 52,
          "start": 379.92,
          "end": 381.06,
          "text": "That's great, thank you."
        },
        {
          "id": 53,
          "start": 381.5,
          "end": 384.02,
          "text": "So, I'll look forward to seeing you tomorrow at"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}